1 WHEREAS, Tianna's teammates Aubrey Porter, Brennon Poullard, and Amir
2 Alsayed anchored their parish to victory; and
3 WHEREAS, since 1997, the elementary fitness meet has served as the Olympic
4 Games for elementary school-aged children in thirty parishes across the state, with more than
5 200,000 students competing for the state fitness crown.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
7 does hereby extend a warm welcome to the members, coaches, and parents of the members
8 of the Lafayette Parish School System's Elementary State Championship Fitness Meet team,
9 and does hereby commend and congratulate them on this amazing achievement.
10 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
11 Lafayette Parish School Board.
